Name: athena-xcluster
Summary: Utilities to display cluster usage status
License: MIT
Group: Applications/Communication

Requires: athena-libXj athena-hesiod

%description
The cview and xcluster utilities display MIT maps and Athena cluster
locations and current cluster usage statistics.

%ifos linux
%triggerin -- setup
grep -s -q ^cview /etc/services \
	|| echo "cview	3704/tcp		# Cluster monitoring" \
		>> /etc/services
%endif
